                <p>Effective October 1, 1966, the functions and staff of the American Consulate at
                    Curitiba are to be reduced. Curitiba will no longer perform any statutory
                    consular operations. Its consular services are to be handled by the Consulate
                    General, São Paulo.</p>
                <p>(FAMC No. 439 of Aug. 24, 1966.)</p>
